name: 6126 kilometres
description: When I drove 6126 Kilometres to reach the end of land, on the edges of the Westfjords. From my series "Running from Something, Looking for Something", I wanted to explore the effects of being isolated from technology, throwing myself into a world of ethereal landscapes devoid of any intentions. Shot in Iceland, 2017 with a Leica M2 / Kodak Tri-X. (https://jonathanliu.net/running/) Part of #HenThousand initiative by John Karel!
